{
  "stem": "18770.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 44.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had some distant relatives there, and we went to stay with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember the trip there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do remember the tremendous difference of living, suddenly, in cramped quarters now with these people, which was so different than the life I, we had lived in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I remember, strangely enough, my-- that's, that was the time when I began to experience feelings of anxiety because I think as a child-- and I think I was pretty sensitive that way anyway-- that I was beginning to pick up the vibes of what the war was about.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what they fused with were ghost stories that a cousin of ours used to tell us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- you know, about witches and goblins and this and that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I, I was terribly, terribly affected by those stories.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Frightened me probably more than any of my other cousins and sister.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, I really-- it would stay with me well into the night.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I think I was picking up the--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the war.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Governess went with us to Chelm.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- I believe it was there that the decision was finally made that she would not be able to continue on with us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a money question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was also a question of, you know, not-- just not being able to keep her anymore, plus the fact that we were going to try to get out of the country.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was essentially my, my parents, my sister and I, plus my uncles and aunts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Altogether, there were about 14 or 15 of us, including my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The youngest of us were my cousin and I were about six.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The oldest were my grandparents, who were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in their 70s, I guess.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
